headline: Is Axon Enterprise Stock's Valuation Justified?
summary: Axon has been a big winner on the market, but its high valuation may give some investors pause.

headline: Has Axon's Recent Growth Outpaced Its Fundamentals Amid Broader Tech Stock Volatility in 2025?
summary: If you are trying to decide what to do with Axon Enterprise stock, you are not alone. This company has been catching the eye of both seasoned investors and newer market watchers for good reason. Over the past year, Axon’s share price has climbed an impressive 79.3%, with an even more remarkable 674.3% surge over the last five years. Even with this strong long-term run, the stock has cooled off a bit recently, dipping 8.5% in the last week and sliding 5.1% over the previous month. Some...
